  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases a stunning butterfly with predominantly black wings adorned with distinctive white spots. The butterfly is perched on a thin, green stem, seemingly blending with its natural environment. The wings exhibit a beautiful iridescent sheen, particularly noticeable along the edges where hints of blue and purple light refract. The texture of the wings appears delicate and slightly crumpled. The background is softly blurred, creating a shallow depth of field and highlighting the butterfly as the central subject. Focus is sharpest on the top and front of the butterfly.",
